msgid "Some services automatically come with deployed servlets on startup. One such service is the CXF servlet running in the $$http://localhost:8181/cxf$$ context. Securing such endpoints can be complicated. One approach, which {project_name} is currently using, is ServletReregistrationService, which undeploys a built-in servlet at startup, enabling you to redeploy it on a context secured by {project_name}."
