msgid "\"S256\" - The SHA256 based PKCE method"
msgstr ""

msgid "messageReceiveTimeout - Set a timeout in milliseconds for waiting for message responses from the Keycloak server. This is used, for example, when waiting for a message during 3rd party cookies check. The default value is 10000."
