msgid "prompt - This parameter allows to slightly customize the login flow on the {project_name} server side. For example enforce displaying the login screen in case of value `login`. See link:{adapterguide_link}#_params_forwarding[Parameters Forwarding Section] for the details and all the possible values of the `prompt` parameter."
