msgid "scope - Used to forward the scope parameter to the {project_name} login endpoint. Use a space-delimited list of scopes. Those typically reference link:{adminguide_link}#_client_scopes[Client scopes] defined on particular client. Note that the scope `openid` will be always be added to the list of scopes by the adapter. For example, if you enter the scope options `address phone`, then the request to {project_name} will contain the scope parameter `scope=openid address phone`."
