msgid "acr - Contains the information about `acr` claim, which will be sent inside `claims` parameter to the {project_name} server. Typical usage is for step-up authentication. Example of use `{ values: [\"silver\", \"gold\"], essential: true }`. See OpenID Connect specification and link:{adminguide_link}#_step-up-flow[Step-up authentication documentation] for more details."
