msgid "For validation, if the token is an access token, the provider's user info service will be invoked to validate the token.  A successful call will mean that the access token is valid.  If the subject token is a JWT and if the provider has signature validation enabled, that will be attempted, otherwise, it will default to also invoking on the user info service to validate the token."
